OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson: 'Paul Quinn could
OL,4,Chave been caught a long time ago'
OL,6,FAndrew Malkinson, who wrongly spent 17
OL,7,Fyears in jail for the rape committed
OL,8,Fby Paul Quinn, has called for those
OL,9,Fresponsible for the miscarriage of
OL,10,Fjustice to be held to account.
OL,12,FSex offender Quinn evaded justice for
OL,13,Fnearly 20 years, but jurors at
OL,14,FManchester Crown Court found him
OL,15,Fguilty of attacking the woman on
OL,16,FFriday (17 April).
OL,18,FNo DNA evidence linked Mr Malkinson to
OL,19,Fthe crime, and he always strenuously
OL,20,Fdenied it, but he went on to serve
OL,21,Fyears behind bars.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
