OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson: 'Paul Quinn could
OL,4,Chave been caught a long time ago'
OL,6,FCommenting on the conviction of Quinn,
OL,7,FMr Malkinson said: "I am content that
OL,8,Fthe right result has finally been
OL,9,Fachieved for the victim, myself and
OL,10,Fthe public.
OL,12,F"But the truth is that if the police
OL,13,Fhad acted as they should have done,
OL,14,FPaul Quinn could have been caught a
OL,15,Flong time ago. Instead, they wanted a
OL,16,Fquick conviction and I was a handy
OL,17,Fpatsy forced to spend over 17 years in
OL,18,Fprison for his horrific crime."
OL,26,@oD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776525067
OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson: 'Paul Quinn could
OL,4,Chave been caught a long time ago'
OL,6,F"All those responsible for allowing
OL,7,Fthis dangerous man to wander free
OL,8,Fwhilst I was locked up must now be
OL,9,Fheld to account."
OL,11,FMr Malkinson's conviction was quashed
OL,12,Fin 2023 after his appeal team forced a
OL,13,Fre-examination of evidence. He first
OL,14,Fappealed against his conviction in
OL,15,F2006, but this was dismissed.
OL,17,FHe then made two more attempts, in
OL,18,F2009 and 2018, to ask the Criminal
OL,19,FCases Review Commission to send his
OL,20,Fcase to the Court of Appeal, but both
OL,21,Fwere rejected.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776525067
OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson: 'Paul Quinn could
OL,4,Chave been caught a long time ago'
OL,6,FHis final attempt in 2021 led to his
OL,7,Fappeal against his conviction being
OL,8,Fallowed by the Court of Appeal.
OL,10,FJames Burley, who led the law charity
OL,11,FAPPEAL's investigation into Andrew
OL,12,FMalkinson's wrongful conviction,
OL,13,Fadded: "The grim reality is that Paul
OL,14,FQuinn could have been caught years ago
OL,15,Fand certainly back in 2012, when his
OL,16,FDNA was uploaded to the national
OL,17,Fdatabase.
OL,26,@uD@HOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776525067
OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson: 'Paul Quinn could
OL,4,Chave been caught a long time ago'
OL,6,F"By that point, the authorities had
OL,7,Ffor some years had a searchable DNA
OL,8,Fprofile recovered from the victim's
OL,9,Fclothing which did not match Mr
OL,10,FMalkinson.
OL,12,F"Yet neither Greater Manchester Police
OL,13,Fnor the Criminal Cases Review
OL,14,FCommission bothered to arrange a
OL,15,Ffurther search of the database until
OL,16,F2022, when APPEAL had presented
OL,17,Ffurther DNA evidence supporting Mr
OL,18,FMalkinson's innocence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776525067
OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson: 'Paul Quinn could
OL,4,Chave been caught a long time ago'
OL,6,F"As a consequence, Mr Malkinson spent
OL,7,Fa further 8 years wrongly imprisoned
OL,8,Fwhilst a violent offender lived
OL,9,Ffreely. New periodic DNA searching
OL,10,Frules must be brought in to ensure
OL,11,Fthis situation is never repeated.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776525067
OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson: 'Paul Quinn could
OL,4,Chave been caught a long time ago'
OL,6,F"To ensure a wrongful conviction like
OL,7,FMr Malkinson's cannot happen again, we
OL,8,Falso call for serious consideration to
OL,9,Fbe given to disallowing prosecutions
OL,10,Fbased solely on unsupported eyewitness
OL,11,Fidentification evidence in future.
OL,12,FCertainly, juries need to be given an
OL,13,Fupdated, strengthened warning about
OL,14,Fthe pitfalls of eyewitness
OL,15,Fidentification evidence.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776525067
OL,3,CAndrew Malkinson: 'Paul Quinn could
OL,4,Chave been caught a long time ago'
OL,6,F"We also call for there to be full,
OL,7,Froutine transparency about the
OL,8,Fcriminal histories of all prosecution
OL,9,Fwitnesses ` so that in future innocent
OL,10,Fpeople like Mr Malkinson are not
OL,11,Fdenied the evidence they need to
OL,12,Fproperly defend themselves, as he was."
OL,14,FGreater Manchester Police and the
OL,15,FCriminal Cases Review Commission have
OL,16,Fbeen approached for comment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
